immaculate Home Minutes from Roosevelt Lake. Enjoy easy access to Roosevelt Lake from this pristine property, perfectly situated on a spacious 1/4-acre lot with ample room for all your recreational vehicles-from a Class A motorhome to a toy hauler or boat. Whether you're looking for a primary residence or the ultimate Arizona getaway, this property offers the flexibility, comfort, and location to make it your adventure basecamp. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath home features an open floor plan ideal for gatherings of any size. The large kitchen, complete with an island and breakfast bar, naturally becomes the heart of the home for family and friends to enjoy. Each bedroom is generously sized, offering plenty of space for additional sleeping arrangements during larger get-togethers. Outside, you'll find exceptional amenities for storage and recreation: 20' x 8' CONEX storage unit - waterproof, rodent-proof, and large enough for ATVs, tools, or gear. 34' x 24' covered carport - fits up to four vehicles or multiple watercraft, complete with three double electrical outlets. Workshop shed with lighting and power outlets ideal for hobbies, repairs, or creative projects. Recent updates include a fresh exterior paint and home leveling within the last two years, and low-maintenance Trex decking built to last for years to come. Located just 1.5 miles from the Schoolhouse Boat Ramp, this property provides unparalleled access to boating, fishing, and water recreation. Nestled in the scenic Sierra Ancha Mountains, you're also a short drive from the Mogollon Rim and the Four Peaks area perfect for hiking, off-roading, and exploring Arizona's great outdoors. With urban conveniences in Globe/Miami just 30 minutes away and Payson's mountain charm nearby, this home offers the best of both worlds: peaceful retreat and convenient access. Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a beautifully maintained home in one of Arizona's most adventure-filled regions.
